item.title: [RS2] High Alcher [my first script]
item.dc:creator: @shangtsung1 shangtsung1
item.description:
@shangtsung1 wrote:

my first script

please give feedback

put how many items you wanna alch
have item you wanna alch in first slot
have nature runes in 3rd or 4th slot
have magic tab open
press run

[scar]program Alcher;
//ShangTsung1’s First script
//im not responsible for any bannings
//use this script as you wish but always
//add credit too shangtsung1
Const
amount = 5; // 1 number under how many items you wanna alch
// eg. if i wanna alch 2 items i would put 1
var
c:integer
;
procedure logout;
begin
MoveMouseSmooth(650,486);
wait(672)
clickmouse(650,486,true);
wait(345)
MoveMouseSmooth(649,377);
wait(500)
clickmouse(649,377,true);
end;

begin
repeat
MoveMouseSmooth(709,327);
wait(500)
clickmouse(709,327,false);
wait(800)
MoveMouseSmooth(596,354);
wait(978)
clickmouse (596,354,true);
wait(903)
MoveMouseSmooth(588,228);
wait(507)
clickmouse(588,228,false);
wait(654)
MoveMouseSmooth(577,260);
wait(862)
clickmouse(577,260,true);
c:=c+1;
wait(2000)
until(c>(amount))
logout;
end.
[/scar]
